Brian Moll https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brian_Moll 0 Brian Percy Moll (19 May 1925 – 9 August 2013) was an English Australian character actor of stage, television and film, director and producer who emigrated to Australia from his native England in 1950. Quitting his job as a publicity officer, he became a professional actor in 1956. He was best known for his soap opera television roles, but also appeared in film and numerous theatre productions.
